    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-07-23T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-07-23T00:00:00-05:00" n="1312"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1312">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">Department of the Army Files: Telegram</note>
                <head>No. 1312<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Acting Chairman of the Interim Committee</hi> (<persName
                        corresp="#p_HGL1" type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Harrison</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the Secretary of War</hi> (<persName
                        corresp="#p_SHL2" type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Stimson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">top secret</hi>
                        <lb/>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">operational priority</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-07-23">23 July
                            1945</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <gloss target="#t_War1">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">War</hi>
                    </gloss> 36792. Secretary of <gloss target="#t_War1">War</gloss>
                    <gloss target="#t_EyesOnly1">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Eyes Only</hi>
                    </gloss> top secret from <persName corresp="#p_HGL1">Harrison</persName>.</p>
                <p>Operation may be possible any time from August 1 depending on state of
                    preparation of patient and condition of atmosphere. From point of view of
                    patient only, some chance August 1 to 3, good chance August 4 to 5 and barring
                    unexpected relapse almost certain before August 10.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
